The influence of the Pr on turbulent heat transfer may be quantitatively analyzed using the numerical model of the turbulent heat diffusivity. For air and water, the relationship between turbulent heat diffusivity and y+ was εh/ν∝(y+)3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
